window.bookSummaryJSON = "Danny's father has been dead for 15 years. But one snowy, drunken evening, he hears his father call to him from outside his door. Then, again, on a rainy night in New Orleans, right after pouring a glass of whiskey. He visits his father's old house, booze in hand, hoping to figure out what exactly is haunting him. \"For Everything There is a Season\" is a short horror story that appears in M.J. Pack's collection <i>Certain Dark Things</i>, also available on Audible.com."; 
